All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public final class VFileSequentialRecord
extends VFileRecord
implements Cloneable

this class holds the record data for all sequentially accessed vfiles. This includes both fixed and variable length records. In the case of variable length files, the location of the next record is always relative to the current record. As a result, it is necessary to "remember" where the next record starts. In the case of fixed length records, the starting location of each record can easily be calculated.
